</node>
<node id="Production Equipment">
  <data key="d0">Production Equipment</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Production equipment is industrial machinery whose failure affects production and qualifies for exemption from working hour restrictions under Article 42.</data>
