  <data key="d0">Labor Safety and Health</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Labor safety and health refers to the protection of workers’ life and health, a core concern justifying emergency exceptions to working hour limits in Article 42.&lt;SEP&gt;Labor safety and health is a regulatory domain concerning occupational safety, hygiene standards, and protective measures for workers.</data>
