  <data key="d0">Contract Effectiveness</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Contract Effectiveness refers to the legal commencement of a collective labor contract’s binding force, triggered automatically if no objection is raised by the Labor Administration Department within fifteen days.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7352b9127a22f0a9251386f17f0f9768</data>
  <data key="d4">/Users/pysama/first_prize_RAG/dataset/labor_law.md</data>
