  <data key="d0">Fifteen-Day Review Period</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Fifteen-Day Review Period is the statutory timeframe during which the Labor Administration Department must review and potentially object to a submitted collective labor contract.</data>
