</node>
<node id="Labor Protection and Working Conditions">
  <data key="d0">Labor Protection and Working Conditions</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Labor protection and working conditions is a mandatory clause covering safety, health, and environmental aspects of employment.</data>
