<node id="Article 38">
  <data key="d0">Article 38</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 38 is a statutory provision concerning rest days and holidays, which certain enterprises may be exempted from applying.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 38 is a provision in Chinese labor law mandating that employers guarantee workers at least one day of rest per week.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8091f80b54e6c94fc8302e0ea487ae6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1b224bc392defbea2ebc9ea123f70db</data>
