<node id="Social Insurance Benefits">
  <data key="d0">Social Insurance Benefits</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Social insurance benefits are statutory entitlements provided to laborers in cases such as retirement, illness, injury, work-related disability, occupational disease, unemployment, and maternity.</data>
