<node id="Occupational Disease">
  <data key="d0">Occupational Disease</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Occupational disease is a health condition caused by work-related hazards, entitling a laborer to social insurance benefits.&lt;SEP&gt;An occupational disease is a health condition caused by work-related hazards and confirmed to result in partial or total loss of working capacity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1005fcbd1306706f050d1a4d82ca943&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e07869d7cd11d05487d341eeabe67b63</data>
