</node>
<node id="Article 73">
  <data key="d0">Article 73</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 73 is a provision in Chinese labor law specifying the circumstances under which laborers are entitled to social insurance benefits and related obligations.</data>
