</edge>
<edge source="Employer" target="Economic Compensation">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The employer is legally obligated to provide economic compensation to the employee upon termination of the labor contract under Articles 24, 26, and 27 of the Labor Law.&lt;SEP&gt;The employer is legally required to provide economic compensation to workers under circumstances defined in Article 91.</data>
  <data key="d9">financial obligation,legal obligation,legal requirement,remedial measure</data>
