<edge source="Employer" target="Social Insurance Premium">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The employer has a legal obligation to pay social insurance premiums on time.&lt;SEP&gt;Employers are legally obligated to pay social insurance premiums into the Social Insurance Fund.</data>
