<edge source="Employer" target="Labor Union">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Labor Union has the right to review and express opinions on the Employer's decision to terminate a labor contract if deemed inappropriate.&lt;SEP&gt;The employer must consult with the labor union before extending working hours.</data>
