  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Article 26 grants the Employer the statutory authority to terminate a labor contract under defined circumstances.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 26 grants employers limited authority to terminate labor contracts, but such authority is suspended under Article 29.</data>
