<edge source="Laborer" target="Labor Contract">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The laborer is a party to the labor contract and is bound by its terms and statutory provisions on termination.&lt;SEP&gt;The laborer is a party to the labor contract and bears the legal obligation to provide written notice before termination.&lt;SEP&gt;The laborer holds the right to terminate the labor contract under the conditions specified in Article 32.</data>
